page.title: 20DATA COLLECTION IN R.STOKE
page.content: Interviews,land cover surveys and documentation of the Mendip Hills area in and around Rodney Stoke were carried out by the following pupils aged 13 and 14. Melanie Body,Rebecca Chinn,Nicola Dermitges,Claire Eastwood Melanie Livesey,Louisa Lloyd-Jones, Katherine van der Meulen,Sara McAllister,Helen Nicklin,Rachel Rabbits,Sally Scourse. Richard Atwell,Marcus Brunton,Robin Covill, Daniel Ford,Justin Gardner,Scott Gould {Paul Klutentreter,}Jason Line,Nigel Loveridge,Paul Manley,Stuart Martin, {James Packer,}Simon Pearson,{Stewart {Richards,}Jonathan White,Darren Wilcox,Robert Williams. Nicola Bunning,Joane Calvert,Lise Curtis, Sally Earnshaw,Lindsay Skidmore,Mark Ewing,Ben Gate,Nicholas Howard,Robert Johnson,Chris Nicklin,John Pickering, Alan Pippett,Ben Whittle.
